{"type": "article", "id": 16687, "title": "滴漏式咖啡器皿", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-28T06:14:49Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 48, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606150630IseK2NSo8nd3cyFg.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是香港 milk design 设计的滴漏式咖啡器皿 H.A.N.D 系列，意为“have a nice day”。包括水壶、滤嘴、玻璃瓶和马克杯一套。使用时需要将 V60 滤纸放在滤嘴里，然后放上咖啡豆，慢慢过滤水进入玻璃瓶中。铜质的水壶和滤嘴自带优雅的气质，水壶能容纳 800 毫升的水，适合初学者在家中自制咖啡。<a href=\"http://www.toastliving.com/products\" target=\"_blank\">这里是他们的主页。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144000JBW6sNiczRT8YbX5.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"1227\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144000rHFP9SOCm0zc5Ei7.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"765\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.93520782\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261440006prvdqcjTBt9NKb8.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"692\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.84596577\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144001zTSwfbsDQKBc9MWA.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"790\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.96577017\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}